Privacy Policy
Our Privacy Policy
Introduction:
Bansemer Consulting GmbH respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you provide through our website. This Privacy Policy applies solely to information we collect via the website and the app.
Website Visitors and App Users:
Like most website operators and App Developers, Bansemer Consulting GmbH collects non-personally-identifying information that mobile devices, computers, web browsers, and servers typically make available, such as device and browser type, language preference, referring site, and the date and time of each visitor request or app crash. Our purpose is to better understand how Bansemer Consulting GmbH's visitors use its website and the app.
Collection of Personally-Identifying Information:
Certain visitors to Bansemer Consulting GmbH's websites choose to interact in ways that require Bansemer Consulting GmbH to gather personally-identifying information. The amount and type of information that Bansemer Consulting GmbH gathers depend on the nature of the interaction. For instance, we ask visitors who sign up for a blog to provide a username and email address. If you send us an email, we will get your email address.
Security:
The security of your personal information is important to us. We strive to protect your personal information but cannot guarantee its absolute security.
Links to External Sites:
Our website may contain links to external sites not operated by us. If you click on a third-party link, you will be directed to that third party's site. We strongly advise you to review the Privacy Policy of every site you visit. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of third-party sites or services.
Aggregated Statistics:
Bansemer Consulting GmbH may collect statistics about the behavior of visitors to its website. However, Bansemer Consulting GmbH does not disclose personally-identifying information.
Cookies:
Bansemer Consulting GmbH uses cookies to identify and track visitors and their usage of this website. Visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Bansemer Consulting GmbH's websites.
Target Audience:
This website is intended exclusively for adults.
Changes to the Privacy Policy:
Bansemer Consulting GmbH may change its Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage visitors to frequently check this page for any changes.
Contact:
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via
email to beratung@bansemer.net
.